ablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; centered_text=&#8221;true&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][nectar_btn size=&#8221;large&#8221; button_style=&#8221;regular&#8221; button_color_2=&#8221;Accent-Color&#8221; icon_family=&#8221;default_arrow&#8221; text=&#8221;Business Assessment for Investment Visa&#8221; url=&#8221;https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/business-immigration-assessment\/&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<h2 id=\"accepted-tests\">What Types of Language Tests are Accepted?<\/h2>\n<p>The <strong>BC PNP<\/strong> accepts the following types of language proficiency tests:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"http:\/\/www.ielts.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">International English Language Testing System (IELTS) General Training<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"http:\/\/www.celpiptest.ca\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Canadian English Language Proficiency Index Program (CELPIP-General)<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.lefrancaisdesaffaires.fr\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Test d&#8217;\u00e9valuation de fran\u00e7ais (TEF)<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ciep.fr\/en\/tcf-canada\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Test de connaissance du fran\u00e7ais (TCF)<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Note that your language test results must be less than two years old to be valid. Depending on the stream, you will need to submit these test results when you are filing your initial BC PNP application or after you have been selected.[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; top_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; bottom_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][image_with_animation image_url=&#8221;12481&#8243; animation=&#8221;Fade In From Right&#8221; hover_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; alignment=&#8221;&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; box_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; image_loading=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; max_width_mobile=&#8221;default&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;padding-6-percent&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;1px&#8221; column_border_color=&#8221;#707070&#8243; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Apply for British Columbia PNP with Licensed Experts<\/h3>\n[\/vc_column_text][nectar_btn size=&#8221;large&#8221; button_style=&#8221;regular&#8221; button_color_2=&#8221;Accent-Color&#8221; icon_family=&#8221;default_arrow&#8221; text=&#8221;Book a consultation&#8221; url=&#8221;https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/book-consultation\/&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;20px&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Language Test Result Conversions&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_id=&#8221;conversion&#8221;][vc_column_text]In some cases, you may be required to convert your language test results to determine what the CLB score is. An example of the test results you would need to score <strong>CLB 4<\/strong> is shown for each test type in the following table:<\/p>\n<table width=\"586\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"82\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"130\"><strong>Listening<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"124\"><strong>Reading<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"125\"><strong>Writing<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"125\"><strong>Speaking<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"82\"><strong>IELTS<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"130\">4.5<\/td>\n<td width=\"124\">3.5<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">4.0<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">4.0<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"82\"><strong>CELPIP<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"130\">4<\/td>\n<td width=\"124\">4<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">4<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">4<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"82\"><strong>TCF<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"130\">331<\/td>\n<td width=\"124\">342<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">4<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">4<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"82\"><strong>TEF<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"130\">145<\/td>\n<td width=\"124\">121<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">181<\/td>\n<td width=\"125\">181<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>The validity of test results is <strong>two years<\/strong> from the date of issuing. Suppose a minimum level of language competence is required for your application. In that case, your test results must also be valid when you submit your application to obtain registration points for your test results.[\/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;BC PNP Language Requirements for Skills Immigration Category&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_id=&#8221;skills-immigration&#8221;][vc_column_text]The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/british-columbia-provincial-nominee-program-bc-pnp\/skills-immigration\/\"><strong>BC PNP Skills Immigration<\/strong><\/a> category encompasses many different programs. This includes<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>BC PNP Skilled Worker<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>BC PNP Health Authority<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>BC PNP International Graduate<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>BC PNP International Post Graduate<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>BC PNP Entry Level and Semi-Skilled<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Some programs require you to possess a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/blog\/get-job-offer-from-outside-canada\/\"><strong>job offer<\/strong><\/a>, while others do not. You will need to meet specific language requirements only if you are applying to a category that requires a job offer.<\/p>\n<h3>Skills Immigration Language Requirements for Job Offers in NOC TEER 2, 3, 4 or 5 Occupations<\/h3>\n<p>Suppose you have a job offer in an occupation that falls under the Canadian National Occupational Classification <strong>NOC TEER 2, 3, 4 or 5<\/strong>. In that case, you will need to score a minimum of CLB 4 in a language proficiency exam.<\/p>\n<h3>Skills Immigration Language Requirements for Job Offers in NOC TEER 0 or 1 Occupations<\/h3>\n<p>If your Canadian job offer is in an occupation that falls under NOC skill levels 0 or A, you don\u2019t need to meet any language requirement.[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; top_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; bottom_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][image_with_animation image_url=&#8221;12475&#8243; animation=&#8221;Fade In From Right&#8221; hover_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; alignment=&#8221;&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; box_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; image_loading=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; max_width_mobile=&#8221;default&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;padding-6-percent&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_bord