ing categories.<\/li>\n<li>Canadian Experience Class: <strong>CLB 7<\/strong> for jobs in <strong>NOC TEER 0 or 1<\/strong>. <strong>CLB 5<\/strong> for jobs in <strong>NOC TEER 2 or 3<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n[\/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;BC PNP Language Requirements for Entrepreneur Immigration&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_id=&#8221;entrepreneur-immigration&#8221;][vc_column_text]The BC PNP includes two <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/british-columbia-provincial-nominee-program-bc-pnp\/entrepreneur-immigration\/\"><strong>Entrepreneur Immigration<\/strong><\/a> categories. The minimum BC PNP requirements for language in each category are as follows:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/british-columbia-provincial-nominee-program-bc-pnp\/entrepreneur-immigration\/base-category\/\"><strong>BC PNP Entrepreneur Base Category<\/strong><\/a>: <strong>CLB 4<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/british-columbia-provincial-nominee-program-bc-pnp\/entrepreneur-immigration\/regional-pilot\/\"><strong>BC PNP Regional Pilot Program<\/strong><\/a>: <strong>CLB 4<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; top_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; bottom_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_di